<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>6</hymn_number>
<title>MATRYRDOM</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Pathien! Nang Lalpen na hi,
 Ka lungthim uh na en;
 Bangkim ka gel leh ngaihtuoh hi,
 Na hetloh a um puo'i.

[V2]
 2. Keinei venna'n sun leh zan in,
 Mitzung Na tuoh ngei puoi;
 Ngaihtuohna thieng ei siemsak in,
 Lalpa Isu ziek in.

[V3]
 3. Na thu thu-a um ka nuom hi,
 Na thu hinna ahi;
 Zeziekchun ei hun hezing in,
 Nangmah mite ka hiu.</lyrics>
</song>